data.description: You do not want to miss seeing this elegant home in the best location. Downtown Bentonville is minutes away with I 49 access as well. You are moments away from all the surrounding areas. Slaughter Pen bike trail access at the end of the street. The spacious living room with open kitchen gives you the cozy feeling you are looking for. You have plenty of room with 3 bedrooms upstairs and master, office and dining room downstairs. This truly is a dream house. Schedule your showing today or come by the Open House on Saturday from 1:00 -3:00.
